node.text:
Where was the bluest water you’ve ever seen with your own eyes? 💦Paradise found by @loucosporviagem in none other than the breathtaking Maldives. 🇲🇻 

Whether your on land or kayaking the seas, you can’t help but soak up the blue and get those paradise feels. From thrilling sports to basking in utter relaxation, you'll be spoiled for choice with the endless things you can do in this destination. 

From diving and kayaking to indulging in luxurious spa treatments, there's something for everyone in this tropical paradise! 🤩

Where was your last beach trip and which beach would you like to go to next? 🏝

🎥 @loucosporviagem
📍 Maldives

Do you prefer to swim in lakes or oceans? 💦 Well here’s the best of both worlds! Crystal clear salt lake ✨ Have you heard about these amazing lakes before? 

China is home to a long list of beautiful salt lakes, including the Chaerhan Salt Lake (the biggest in China), and the Xiechi Lake, known for its vibrant shades of yellow, green and magenta due to algal blooms. Would you visit one of these lakes? 

#discoverChina
🎥 by VIP00525 on Tiktok
